invalid type: string "Medical Reference: Wrinkles (Rhytids) \n1\u{fe0f}. Condition Overview \nName: Wrinkles (Rhytids) Definition: Wrinkles are lines, folds, or creases that form in the skin as a natural \npart of the aging process. They are primarily caused by the degradation of structural proteins—specifically \nn for high-strength Tretinoin or topical anti-androgens (e.g., \nClascoterone). \n